keywords:
  - abundance
  - narrative dataset
  - AI reasoning
  - conditional optimism
  - knowledge architecture
  - agent augmentation
  - RAG
  - benchmark

abstract: >-
  The Abundance Codex is an open-source narrative dataset of 63 entries across
  21 Grand Challenge domains, designed to shift AI agent reasoning from
  scarcity-default to evidence-anchored abundance. Evaluated via the ACE
  benchmark (2,016 cross-model judgments), augmented models show +9%
  improvement in reasoning quality, with cost-efficient models showing
  3-4x larger gains than frontier models.
